OL,6,FTanker drivers supplying garage
OL,7,Fforecourts and aviation fuel are to go
OL,8,Fon strike in a dispute over pay.
OL,10,FMembers of Unite based at Stanlow oil
OL,11,Frefinery will walk out from June 6-8
OL,12,Fand 13-15 which the union said will
OL,13,Faffect deliveries across the North
OL,14,FWest of England and the Scottish
OL,15,FBorders.
OL,17,FThe drivers, who work for Hoyer `
OL,18,Frecently rebranded as Oxalis ` say
OL,19,Ftheir pay offer is significantly lower
OL,20,Fthan that of their colleagues in other
OL,21,Fparts of the country.
