OL,6,FThe company said it has contingency
OL,7,Fplans so that its operations can
OL,8,Fcontinue.
OL,10,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,11,Fsaid: "Oxalis is treating its Stanlow-
OL,12,Fbased drivers as second-class workers.
OL,14,F"There is absolutely no reason why
OL,15,Fthis profitable company should not be
OL,16,Fpaying these workers the same rates as
OL,17,Fpay as their colleagues based
OL,18,Felsewhere.
OL,20,F"They will receive Unite's total
OL,21,Fsupport as they strike for equal pay."
