OL,6,FAn Oxalis spokesperson said: "Oxalis
OL,7,Fhas offered drivers a 19% pay increase
OL,8,Fover two years. Any further increase
OL,9,Fseverely compromises the viability of
OL,10,Fthe operation and puts jobs at risk.
OL,12,F"Further talks are planned with the
OL,13,Funion and whilst we hope we can reach
OL,14,Fa mutually agreeable deal, contingency
OL,15,Fplans are fully developed and we are
OL,16,Fconfident all our operations will
OL,17,Fcontinue should industrial action take
OL,18,Fplace."
